rtially), [[Mulberry Grove, Illinois|Mulberry Grove]], [[Old Ripley, Illinois|Old Ripley]], [[Panama, Illinois|Panama]], [[Pierron, Illinois|Pierron]], [[Pocahontas, Illinois|Pocahontas]], [[Smithboro, Illinois|Smithboro]], [[Sorento, Illinois|Sorento]]\n* '''Calhoun County IL:''' [[Brussels, Illinois|Brussels]], [[Hardin, Illinois|Hardin]], [[Kampsville, Illinois|Kampsville]]\n* '''Clinton County IL:''' [[Albers, Illinois|Albers]], [[Aviston, Illinois|Aviston]], [[Bartelso, Illinois|Bartelso]], [[Beckemeyer, Illinois|Beckemeyer]], [[Breese, Illinois|Breese]], [[Carlyle, Illinois|Carlyle]], [[Centralia, Illinois|Centralia]] (partial), [[Damiansville, Illinois|Damiansville]], [[Germantown, Illinois|Germantown]], [[Hoffman, Illinois|Hoffman]], [[Huey, Illinois|Huey]], [[Keyesport, Illinois|Keyesport]] (partially), [[New Baden, Illinois|New Baden]], [[Saint Rose, Illinois|St. Rose]], [[Shattuc, Illinois|Shattuc]], [[Trenton, Illinois|Trenton]], [[Wamac, Illinois|Wamac]] (partially)\n* '''Jersey County IL:''' [[Brighton, Illinois|Brighton]] (partially), [[Elsah, Illinois|Elsah]], [[Fidelity, Illinois|Fidelity]], [[Fieldon, Illinois|Fieldon]], [[Grafton, Illinois|Grafton]], [[Jerseyville, Illinois|Jerseyville]], [[Otterville, Illinois|Otterville]]\n* '''Macoupin County IL:''' [[Benld, Illinois|Benld]], [[Brighton, Illinois|Brighton]] (mostly), [[Bunker Hill, Illinois|Bunker Hill]], [[Carlinville, Illinois|Carlinville]], [[Chesterfield, Illinois|Chesterfield]], [[Dorchester, Illinois|Dorchester]], [[East Gillespie, Illinois|East Gillespie]], [[Gillespie, Illinois|Gillespie]], [[Girard, Illinois|Girard]], [[Mount Olive, Illinois|Mt. Olive]], [[Medora, Illinois|Medora]], [[Modesto, Illinois|Modesto]], [[Mount Clare, Illinois|Mount Clare]], [[Nilwood, Illinois|Nilwood]], [[Royal Lakes, Illinois|Royal Lakes]], [[Sawyerville, Illinois|Sawyerville]], [[Shipman, Illinois|Shipman]], [[Staunton, Illinois|Staunton]], [[Virden, Illinois|Virden]] (partial), [[White City, Illinois|Whi