mjagran.org/}}</ref> and their coordinating committee \"Dharam Jagaran Samanvay Samiti\"<ref name=\"Ten-most\" /><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/rss-body-dharam-jagran-samiti-sets-fixed-rates-converting-muslims-christians-into-hindus-616924 |title=RSS Body Dharam Jagran Samiti Sets Fixed Rates for Converting Muslims, Christians into Hindus}}</ref>\n* [[Muslim Rashtriya Manch]], '' National Front of [[Muslims]]''\n* Rashtriya Hindu Andolan, ''based in [[Maharashtra]] calls for the deletion of \"secular\" from the Indian Constitution''<ref name=\"Ten-most\" />\n* [[Rashtriya Sikh Sangat]], ''a sociocultural organisation with the aim to spread the knowledge of [[Gurbani]] to the Indian society.''{{sfn|Chitkara|2004|p=168}}\n* Hindu Rashtra Sena, ''propagating for the establishment of Hindu Rashtra.''<ref name=\"Ten-most\" /><ref name=\"No-bail\">{{Cite news |author=Thomas, Shibu |title=Hate speech: Bombay high court denies bail to Hindu Sena chief |date=29 March 2015 |newspaper=[[The Times of India]] |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Hate-speech-Bombay-high-court-denies-bail-to-Hindu-Sena-chief/articleshow/46731600.cms |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402015135/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Hate-speech-Bombay-high-court-denies-bail-to-Hindu-Sena-chief/articleshow/46731600.cms |archivedate=2 April 2015 |url-status=live |df=dmy }}</ref>\n\n;Regional based \n* [[Hindu Munnani]], ''a religio-cultural organization based in Tamil Nadu.''<ref name=\"Thirumaavalavan2003\">{{citation |author=Thirumaavalavan |title=Talisman, Extreme Emotions of Dalit Liberation |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=VsE2KwKwh0YC&pg=PA55 |year=2003 |publisher=Popular Prakashan |isbn=978-81-85604-68-8 |pages=55\u2013}}</ref>\n* [[Hindu Aikya Vedi]], ''Hindu United Front'' based in Kerala<ref>[http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/kerala/rss-to-infuse-young-blood-into-bjp/article8047586.ece RSS to infuse young blood into Kerala BJP], The Hindu, 31 D