le=Best of times for the RSS, it aims for makeover at 90}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://main.hindusthansamachar.com/ |title=Welcome to Hindusthan Samachar |work=hindusthansamachar.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://hindustansamachar.in/ |title=Home |work=Hindustan Samachar |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217080050/http://hindustansamachar.in/ |archivedate=17 December 2014 |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n\n;Think Tanks\n* Bharatiya Vichara Kendra, ''General Think Tank.''\n* Hindu Vivek Kendra, ''a resource center for the promotion of the ideology of [[Hindutva]]''.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hvk.org/about.html |title=Hindu Vivek Kendra |work=hvk.org}}</ref>\n* [[Vivekananda Kendra]], promotion of [[Swami Vivekananda]]'s ideas with [[Vivekananda International Foundation]] in New Delhi as a \"Public Policy Think Tank\" with 6 Centres of study.\n* India Policy Foundation, ''a not-for-profit Think Tank''<ref>{{Cite web |title=About India Policy Foundation |date=5 July 2014 |publisher=India Policy Foundation |url=http://www.indiapolicyfoundation.org/encyc/2014/7/5/About-India-Policy-Foundation.aspx |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150214051947/http://www.indiapolicyfoundation.org/encyc/2014/7/5/About-India-Policy-Foundation.aspx |archivedate=14 February 2015 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n* Bharatiya Shikshan Mandal, ''a Think Tank on educational reforms.''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bsmbharat.org/ |title=Welcome to Bhartiya Shikshan Mandal |work=bsmbharat.org}}</ref>\n* India Foundation, ''a Think Tank''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/rise-of-the-right-wing-intelligentsia-in-search-of-an-alternative-universe-of-ideas/article1-1303666.aspx |title=Right wing groups woo world for their idea of India |work=hindustantimes.com/}}</ref>\n* [[Akhil Bharatiya Itihas Sankalan Yojana]] (ABISY), ''All-India history reform project''\n* Syama Prasad Mookerjee Research Foundation (SPMRF)<ref>{{cite web |last1=Peri |f