om/ps3/games/detail/item410782/Bleach-Soul-Resurrecci%C3%B3n/|title=Bleach: Soul Resurrecci\u00f3n|publisher=[[PlayStation]]|accessdate=May 30, 2014}}</ref>\n|release=2011\u2014[[PlayStation 3]]<ref name=\"Ignition\"/>\n|notes=* An [[Action game|action]] video game<ref name=\"Ignition\"/>\n* Developed by [[SCE Japan Studio]] and [[Racjin]], and published by SCEI<ref name=\"Ignition\"/>\n* The initial release came with three downloadable anime episodes of ''[[Bleach (anime)|Bleach]]'' (episodes 190\u2013192) from [[PlayStation Network]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nisamerica.com/nart/pbombs/2011/156/Bleach_release_20110802_final2pb.pdf|title=Bleach: Soul Resurrecci\u00f3n|publisher=[[Nippon Ichi Software|NIS America]]|accessdate=May 30, 2014}}</ref>\n* Released under ''The Best'' label on January 24, 2013 in Japan<ref name=\"Ignition2\">{{cite web|url=http://www.jp.playstation.com/software/title/bcjs70025.html|title=Bleach \u30bd\u30a6\u30eb\u30fb\u30a4\u30b0\u30cb\u30c3\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3 PlayStation\u00ae3 the Best|publisher=[[PlayStation]]|language=Japanese|accessdate=May 30, 2014}}</ref>\n}}\n{{Video game titles/item\n|title=Bleach: Bankai Batoru\n|date= {{vgrelease|JP|April 14, 2014}}\n|refs=<ref name=\"Bankai Battle\">{{cite web|url=http://corp.gree.net/jp/ja/news/press/2014/0414-01.html|title=\u30b0\u30ea\u30fc\u3068ORATTA\u306e\u5171\u540c\u958b\u767a\u30bf\u30a4\u30c8\u30eb\u300cBLEACH \u534d\u89e3\u30d0\u30c8\u30eb\u300d4\u670814\u65e5\u3088\u308a\u63d0\u4f9b\u958b\u59cb|publisher=GREE, Inc.|language=Japanese|date=April 14, 2014|accessdate=May 2, 2014}}</ref>\n|release=2014\u2014[[iOS]],<ref name=\"Bankai Battle\"/> [[Android (operating system)|Android]]<ref name=\"Bankai Battle\"/>\n|notes=* A [[Social network game|social network]] based video game<ref name=\"Bankai Battle\"/>\n* Developed by ORATTA and published by [[GREE, Inc.|GREE]]<ref name=\"Bankai Battle\"/>\n}}\n{{Video game titles/item\n|title=Bleach: Brave Souls\n|article=Bleach: Brave Souls\n|date= 